  "instruction": "Evaluate the limit by factoring: lim(x->\\1) ({a}(x^2 - {r}^2)) / (x - {r}).",
  "params": {
    "a": {
      "type": "int",
      "min": 1,
      "max": 4
    },
    "r": {
      "type": "int",
      "min": 1,
      "max": 6
    }
  },
  "answer_expr": "limit_factor210",
  "steps": [
    "Factor the numerator: {a}(x^2 - {r}^2) = {a}(x + {r})(x - {r}).",
    "Cancel (x - {r}): limit = {a}(x + {r}).",
    "Substitute x = {r}: {a}({r} + {r}) = {answer_limit_factor210}."
  ],
  "tags": [
    "calculus",
    "limits",
